<Base title="Quarry — Support" doc>
  <nav><a href="/quarry/">← Quarry</a></nav>
  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days. Or message us on <a href="https://t.me/sunpebble">Telegram</a>.</p>

  <h2>Install Quarry</h2>
  <p>Download the latest <code>Quarry-*.zip</code> from
     <a href="https://github.com/sunpebble/quarry/releases">GitHub Releases</a>, unzip it,
     and move <code>Quarry.app</code> to your Applications folder.</p>

  <h2>Connection issues</h2>
  <p>For local SQLite or SQLCipher files, confirm the file path and password. For PostgreSQL or MySQL,
     confirm the host, port, database name, and any SSH tunnel settings.</p>

  <h2>Build from source</h2>
  <p>Developer setup lives in the <a href="https://github.com/sunpebble/quarry#build-from-source">Quarry README</a>.</p>
</Base>
